title: Bigfoot devotees swap tales at NY expo: 'I think he came to my house that night'
text:
Bigfoot devotees swap tales at NY expo: 'I think he came to my house that night' 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
About 100 people sported buttons saying "I believe" and swapped stories at the fourth annual Chautauqua Lake Bigfoot Expo....
